---
import PageLayout from '~/layouts/PageLayout.astro';
const metadata = {
  title: 'Privacy Policy',
  ignoreTitleTemplate: true,
};
const pageTitle = 'Privacy Policy';
---

<PageLayout metadata={metadata} hasPageHeader pageTitle={pageTitle} highlightedTitleText="Privacy">
  <main class="max-w-5xl px-4 py-10 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 lg:py-14 mx-auto font-sans prose">
    <header>
      <p><small>Last Updated: January 2, 2025</small></p>
    </header>

    <section>
      <h2>Introduction</h2>
      <p>
        Pursuant to the Personal Data Protection Act 2010 (PDPA) of Malaysia, this Privacy Policy explains how we
        collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your personal data. This policy applies to all personal data processed by
        us, and by engaging with our services, you acknowledge that you have read and understood this policy.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Notice and Choice Principle</h2>
      <p>
        In accordance with the PDPA, we hereby inform you that your personal data will be processed by us or on our
        behalf. By providing your personal data to us, you consent to the processing of your personal data in accordance
        with this Privacy Policy.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
      <article>
        <h3>Personal Data</h3>
        <p>We collect and process the following personal data when you:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Register on our website</li>
          <li>Subscribe to our newsletter</li>
          <li>Fill out a form</li>
          <li>Send us an email</li>
          <li>Use our services</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Personal data may include:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Name and NRIC number (where required by law)</li>
          <li>Contact details including address</li>
          <li>Email address</li>
          <li>Phone number</li>
          <li>Payment information</li>
          <li>Company information</li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <article>
        <h3>Automatically Collected Information</h3>
        <p>When you visit our website, we automatically collect:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>IP address</li>
          <li>Browser type</li>
          <li>Operating system</li>
          <li>Access times</li>
          <li>Pages viewed</li>
          <li>Links clicked</li>
        </ul>
      </article>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Purpose of Processing Personal Data</h2>
      <p>Your personal data is processed for the following purposes:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Providing and improving our services</li>
        <li>Processing your transactions</li>
        <li>Sending you marketing communications (with your consent)</li>
        <li>Responding to your inquiries</li>
        <li>Complying with legal obligations</li>
        <li>Managing our business operations</li>
        <li>Detecting and preventing fraud</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Disclosure of Personal Data</h2>
      <article>
        <h3>Third-Party Service Providers</h3>
        <p>We may disclose your personal data to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Payment processors</li>
          <li>Data analytics providers</li>
          <li>Email service providers</li>
          <li>Hosting services</li>
          <li>Customer service providers</li>
          <li>Marketing service providers</li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <article>
        <h3>Legal Requirements</h3>
        <p>We may disclose your personal data where required:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>By Malaysian law or regulation</li>
          <li>To protect our rights or property</li>
          <li>To prevent or investigate possible wrongdoing</li>
          <li>To protect public safety</li>
        </ul>
      </article>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Security of Personal Data</h2>
      <p>
        We implement appropriate security measures as required by the PDPA to protect your personal data from
        unauthorized access, modification, or disclosure. These measures are regularly reviewed and updated.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Data Subject Rights</h2>
      <p>Under the PDPA, you have the right to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Request access to your personal data</li>
        <li>Request correction of inaccurate personal data</li>
        <li>Withdraw consent for processing</li>
        <li>Request information about our data processing policies</li>
        <li>Limit the processing of your personal data</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Retention of Personal Data</h2>
      <p>
        We retain personal data only for as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes outlined in this policy, or as
        required by Malaysian law. When personal data is no longer necessary, it will be securely deleted or anonymized.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Cross-Border Transfer</h2>
      <p>
        If we transfer your personal data outside Malaysia, we will ensure compliance with the PDPA requirements for
        cross-border transfers and ensure that your personal data receives adequate protection in the recipient country.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Use of Cookies</h2>
      <p>Our website uses cookies and similar technologies to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Enhance user experience</li>
        <li>Remember your preferences</li>
        <li>Analyze website traffic</li>
        <li>Provide personalized content</li>
      </ul>
      <p>You may configure your browser settings to manage cookie preferences.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Changes to Privacy Policy</h2>
      <p>
        We reserve the right to update this privacy policy in compliance with the PDPA and other applicable laws. Any
        changes will be posted on this page with an updated revision date.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Contact Information</h2>
      <address>
        <p>
          Wahine Capital Sdn Bhd<br />
          Suite B9-07, Plaza Mont Kiara, 2 Jalan Kiara, Mont Kiara, 50480 Kuala Lumpur, Wilayah Persekutuan Kuala Lumpur<br />
          Email: <a href="mailto:privacy@company.com">hellowahine@wcapital.asia</a><br />
        </p>
        <p>
          For privacy-related inquiries or to exercise your rights under the PDPA, please contact us at the above address.
        </p>
      </address>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Governing Law</h2>
      <p>
        This Privacy Policy is governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of Malaysia, particularly the
        Personal Data Protection Act 2010.
      </p>
    </section>
  </main>
</PageLayout>
